textAfterTable: Greek Life greek life is no fairy tale. our sororities are the elite and high achievers, there are no kegs and sorority houses here. Clubs and Activities this is a pretty mellow town, nothing big city, but we are around a cool beach atmosphere and very environmental. Great for these types of students if you are the average small town california kid with a taste for the beach and outdoors, cabrillo is the school for you. Share any unusual traditions or locations on campus no unusual traditions. most people keep to themselves this isn't a very large college, but there are bands that play on the quad every once in a while. Bang for the buck if you're from around the area it's cheap. outside cali, the thing gets harder. almost all local cali students receive financial aid here that will cover more than enough for tuition.
